metadata.name: Colors of Ethereal
metadata.description:
Sharing my first photo in Brazilian waters in a glamorous sunset seascape. 

This photo is so much mean to me because this is my first travel in other parts of the world. and the sunset colors is so unrealistic .

This Photo was taken in Itaqui, Brazil.

Please Support my Collection so I can showcase more extravagant photos. Who ever get this photo will receive  my signature preset.
